    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330540/extras/b6af9e13514380eaba17596a12e3cb2a.avif?t=1742834038\" width=800 height=374 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Leap into a 2.5D action platformer that takes inspiration from the iconic gameplay of the old-school <i>Prince of Persia</i> games, but upgrades it with a unique swashbuckling combat system.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Keep your wits as sharp as your blade, for only the most heroic, dashing, and (most importantly) <i>stylish</i> of swordmasters will make it out alive!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330540/extras/ac05036fb7a6b08afd91d84843ec3b7c.avif?t=1742834038\" width=800 height=97 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330540/extras/a0fe284b90d94e03bb69b456cc5c489c.poster.avif?t=1742834038\" width=600 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330540/extras/a0fe284b90d94e03bb69b456cc5c489c.webm?t=1742834038\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330540/extras/a0fe284b90d94e03bb69b456cc5c489c.mp4?t=1742834038\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Earn style by fighting with flair - swing from chandeliers, trick enemies into attacking each other, kick bottles into your enemies, and any other clever maneuvers you can find. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Then use your Style to dazzle your enemies with powerful special abilities, turning the tables on even the most powerful foes!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330540/extras/3f99d5f546ef38486225d9db89b476b0.avif?t=1742834038\" width=800 height=97 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330540/extras/5b18d98284561ec26c72864fa38cbcf5.poster.avif?t=1742834038\" width=600 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330540/extras/5b18d98284561ec26c72864fa38cbcf5.webm?t=1742834038\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330540/extras/5b18d98284561ec26c72864fa38cbcf5.mp4?t=1742834038\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Each level is designed to encourage exploration, with mysterious secrets hidden throughout. Paths are interwoven, and every twist and turn can reveal either a marvelous new surprise... or a deadly trap.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330540/extras/d8e5b9c64d97ae5d56b4a57b8c927e16.avif?t=1742834038\" width=800 height=97 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330540/extras/4374d02d9004f3a1f850aafd03e8f88d.poster.avif?t=1742834038\" width=600 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330540/extras/4374d02d9004f3a1f850aafd03e8f88d.webm?t=1742834038\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330540/extras/4374d02d9004f3a1f850aafd03e8f88d.mp4?t=1742834038\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Every room of the Palace is a handcrafted work of art, but the dangers within will change each time you fail. You must stay on your toes if you are to survive its perils!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330540/extras/bfea49756cde3b117aa7e436e1053e56.avif?t=1742834038\" width=800 height=97 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330540/extras/fffa571944f91df37e0bb9d87de21a95.poster.avif?t=1742834038\" width=600 height=282 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330540/extras/fffa571944f91df37e0bb9d87de21a95.webm?t=1742834038\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330540/extras/fffa571944f91df37e0bb9d87de21a95.mp4?t=1742834038\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >You are Rodrigo Al-Ahzab, a lowly beggar whose only aim is to survive in the streets of Granada. When you are pulled into a magical book, you learn that there are things that matter to you even more than your own survival… </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Created by one of the writers behind <i>SpecOps: The Line</i>, this is a story with depths hidden behind the simple facade... </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
